      • setBehaviorToSubConstructs

        public void setBehaviorToSubConstructs(ClaimBehaviorDefinition currentBehavior)
        Function used after the identification of a behavior by the parser, in order to set the field myBehavior to all the Claim constructs that belong to the specified behavior, in order to give them access to the symbol table.
        Parameters:
        currentBehavior - - the behavior that was read by the parser

      • setBehaviorRecursively

        public void setBehaviorRecursively(ClaimConstruct currentConstruct,
                          ClaimBehaviorDefinition currentBehavior)
        Function used by the method setBehaviorToSubConstructs(ClaimBehaviorDefinition) in order to set the field myBehavior to the current constructs and to all the constructs that are included in it
        Parameters:
        currentConstruct - - the construct to be modified
        currentBehavior - - the behavior that was read by the parser

      • fillSymbolTable

        public void fillSymbolTable(ClaimBehaviorDefinition currentBehavior)
        Function used after the creation of the agent definition object, in order to populate the symbol table with variables (which are unbound, for the moment)
        Parameters:
        currentBehavior - - the behavior which is used as scope for the symbol table

      • fillSymbolTableRecursively

        public void fillSymbolTableRecursively(ClaimConstruct currentConstruct)
        Function used by the method fillSymbolTable(ClaimBehaviorDefinition) in order to put the variables that belong to a behavior in the corresponding symbol table
        Parameters:
        currentConstruct - - the construct which is analyzed in order to be put in the symbol table

      • verifyVariablesInStructure

        public boolean verifyVariablesInStructure(ClaimStructure structure)
        Verifies if the structure given as argument, or any of its substructures, has at least one variable. This function is useful in the case of statements like ForAllk, where passing a structure without any variable doesn't make sense.
        Parameters:
        structure - - the structure to be verified
